 Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a02df27967ec5c859f03303184c08188fa3d5b5","tid":1538602,"uid":241904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:28:41.000Z","msg":"佢而家撤回根本係想我地8/9少人出黎,咁9/9美國復會就未必過到香港人權關係法<br />\n撤回係3個月前既訴求<br />\n而家係五大訴求,缺一不可<br />\n如果唔係只會每幾年就有一過revolution"},{"pid":"c4527960aff8e4fef1314798a781719770d53383","tid":1538602,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4791a96eaa0283d2f5863a57b0a7ffc05f4a910b","tid":1538602,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:31:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c6187bd30e8d70a1ead0446db92b1b229556fa2","tid":1538602,"uid":255962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07