na.cx%2Fi%2FPEJqrg0.jpg&h=789c65ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61fa2fd44e11922d2cb85363deef618ed8aff516","tid":1538602,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:09:13.000Z","msg":"去美國領事館大叫<br />\nChina! Liar!"},{"pid":"4a76a698f6e3cd560d671b052e0b226520473ba4","tid":1538602,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:09:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d9fc539cdded5f086d13323827f25f3531291ba4","tid":1538602,"uid":2479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:09:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n9月8 要人</span><br />\n<br />\n全世界9月8號出俾佢睇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538569</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">入嚟推 大把文宣</span>"},{"pid":"4dd29ba08d4a80c954b2f5882756cd8f812d3cfc","tid":1538602,"uid":193972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:49:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rj6bykzlOaM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRj6bykzlOaM&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEq29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=e9f8f86a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rj6bykzlOaM</a><br />\n去美領記得除左美國國歌, 仲要播埋呢首歌！<br />\n<br />\nThe Battle Hymn of the Republic<br />\n<br />\nMine eyes have seen the glory of the coming of the Lord;<br />\nHe is trampling out the vintage where the grapes of wrath are stored;<br />\nHe hath loosed the fateful lightning of His terrible swift sword;<br />\nHis truth is marching on.<br />\nGlory! Glory! Hallelujah!<br />\nGlory! Glory! Hallelujah!<br />\nGlory! Glory! Hallelujah!<br />\nHis truth is marching on.<br />\nI have seen Him in the watch-fires of a hundred circling camps;<br />\nThey have builded Him an altar in the evening dews and damps;<br />\nI can read His righteous sentence by the dim and flaring lamps,<br />\nHis day is marching on.<br />\nI have read His fiery gospel writ in rows of burnished steel!<br />\n&quot;As ye deal with my condemners, so with you My grace shall deal!<br />\nLet the Hero, born of woman, crush the serpent with his heel, &quot;<br />\nSince God is marching on.<br />\nHe has sounded forth the trumpet that shall never call retreat;<br />\nHe is sifting out the hearts of men before His judgment seat;<br />\nOh, be swift, my soul, to answer Him; be jubilant, my feet!<br />\nOur God is marching on.<br />\nIn the beauty of the lilies Christ was born across the sea,<br />\nWith a glory in His bosom that transfigures you and me;<br />\nAs He died to make men holy, let us die to make men free!<br />\nWhile God is marching on."},{"pid":"f0fcf4c279a75b591d240d59df1887df7a8a6ba2","tid":1538602,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:51:07.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"7c9ca85e2b22fe70c26bd9323ab6ab1e83d25d49","tid":1538602,"uid":298158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:52:14.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n9月8日，美國領事館見！"}]}